msItem.title: Histoire de Lizette et de Colin

supportDesc.extent: 133 leaves : 185 x 128 (137 x 84) mm. bound to 192 x 135 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, vi (contemporary paper) + 133 + vi (contemporary paper); [1-133]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.
